00:58:58.621 --> 00:59:01.321
Prepušten si sebi, čoveče.

00:59:02.041 --> 00:59:06.253
Brže, Peri!
Više brzine!

00:59:06.379 --> 00:59:09.749
Ova krntija brže ne može.

00:59:12.844 --> 00:59:15.544
SENT MORIC, ŠVAJCARSKA

00:59:20.434 --> 00:59:25.961
Edvards, četrdeset devet metara.
